{"tid":828692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慎入！女子脫褲大便　男子為賺錢貼近張口接","createTime":"2018-09-20T01:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T02:28:09.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7acbafb3250c24479a0c45d5857b906f248c03e8","tid":828692,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:07:43.000Z","msg":"奈及利亞男子為了賺錢，張口吃女子大下的大便。<br />\n<br />\n據奈及利亞《pulse》報導，famousblogng在《推特》分享影片指出，一名從事網路詐欺的男子(奈及利亞稱為Yahoo boy)為了賺錢，躺在一名女子的兩腿間，而女子脫褲子大便，讓男子張開口接住這些大便。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，日前一位奈及利亞女子烏蘿娜(Barbie Ulonna)，在臉書上分享她跟從事網路詐欺的前男友約會過程，稱她跟前男友接吻以後，發現嘴巴有瘡傷，就醫後也讓她感到疑惑，為何發生這樣的病狀，後來到前男友家聚會，她在廚房找東西喝時，聽到前男友跟朋友在客廳聊天，發現前男友為了錢吃大便，讓她不僅嚇呆，也知道為何嘴巴會有瘡傷。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180920/1433069/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180920%2F1433069%2F&d=9HFwKgiXanrvJ1lsAHvQR9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=0377a600\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180920%2F1433069%2F&h=bce8d813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180920/1433069/</a>"},{"pid":"ef6e23f229b6d656af0d4ee0750edf1a0d610198","tid":828692,"uid":35852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:14:51.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a1f5b28f56ebab3e14753af20277c42134adc2","tid":828692,"uid":13653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:17:55.000Z","msg":"No thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd00b504f89692f9fb86ff1e163f85182fd84b83","tid":828692,"uid":189109,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/42a/2f4/42a2f43f